icinity of Tc, where theoretical and experimental researches are difficult to\ncarry out. The differences between the obtained results and the earlier\npublished results for T>Tc are discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 25 Feb 2020 19:26:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-27"}
