fects on the highest possible level. The\ndeveloped technique of laser-photodetachment spectroscopy of radioisotopes\nopens the path for future EA measurements of other radioelements such as\npolonium, and eventually super-heavy elements, which are produced at a\none-atom-at-a-time rate.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 26 Feb 2020 11:40:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 28 Feb 2020 14:22:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-26"}
