ons, our work shows that magnetic fields play a key role for the\nprimordial IMF, potentially even more so than for the present-day IMF.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 26 Feb 2020 14:07:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 30 Jun 2020 12:38:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-08"}
